section.section:
The regulations shall:
Require the director of a forensic laboratory to establish and administer an ongoing quality assurance program using standards acceptable to the Secretary;
Require the director of a forensic laboratory to retain all case files for at least 10 years;
Establish qualifications for the personnel of forensic laboratories;
Establish procedures for verifying the background and education of the personnel of forensic laboratories;
Require the Secretary to charge fees that may not exceed the actual direct and indirect costs to the Department to carry out the provisions of this subtitle; and
Establish any additional standards that the Secretary considers necessary to assure that forensic laboratories provide accurate and reliable services.
